---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Our Mission — Helping You Master Scrabble & Sharpen Your Mind" description="ScrabbleWordsFinder.com exists to help everyone get better at Scrabble, build vocabulary, improve memory, and keep their mind sharp. Free tools, games, and AI coaching for players at every level." keywords="scrabble mission, improve vocabulary, cognitive health word games, scrabble training tools, memory improvement, word games brain health, scrabble practice, tournament preparation">

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-4 pb-16">

  <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">Our Mission</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-purple-300 font-medium mb-8">Helping you master words, sharpen your mind, and fall in love with the game.</p>

  <!-- Hero statement -->
  <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-purple-500/40 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-950/30 to-indigo-950/20 p-8 mb-10">
    <p class="text-xl text-white font-light leading-relaxed text-center">
      We believe that <span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">every word you learn</span> makes you a better player, a sharper thinker, and a more confident communicator. ScrabbleWordsFinder.com exists to make that journey <span class="text-green-400 font-semibold">free, fun, fast, and accessible — no sign-up needed</span> to everyone.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Why Scrabble Matters -->
  <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why Scrabble Matters — More Than Just a Game</h2>

  <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Scrabble isn't just tiles on a board. It's a workout for your brain — one that builds vocabulary, strengthens pattern recognition, improves strategic thinking, and keeps your mind agile at any age.</p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-6">
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl mb-1">🧠</p>
      <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Cognitive Health</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Studies link word games to reduced risk of cognitive decline and improved working memory</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/10 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl mb-1">📚</p>
      <p class="text-blue-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Vocabulary Growth</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Active players learn 5-10 new words per week — that compounds to thousands over a year</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl mb-1">🎯</p>
      <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Strategic Thinking</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Every turn is a decision under pressure — weighing risk, reward, and rack management</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Whether your intention is to crush your family at game night, keep your mind healthy as you age, prepare for your first tournament, or simply enjoy the satisfaction of finding the perfect word — <strong class="text-white">ScrabbleWordsFinder.com has something for you.</strong></p>

  <!-- What We Offer -->
  <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Everything You Need — All Free, All Instant</h2>

  <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">We've built a complete ecosystem of tools, games, and learning resources. No sign-up. No paywall. No limits. Just pure Scrabble improvement at your fingertips.</p>

  <!-- Tool: Word Solver -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/10 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="text-lg">🔍</span>
      <h3 class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">The Word Solver</h3>
      <a href="/" class="ml-auto text-xs text-blue-400 hover:underline">Try it →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Enter your 7 tiles and instantly see every valid word you can make — ranked by score, with tile probability, rack leave analysis, and opening move suggestions. Results appear as you type. No waiting, no page reloads. This is where improvement begins: seeing the words you missed teaches you what to look for next time.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tool: Memory WordBench -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="text-lg">🃏</span>
      <h3 class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Memory WordBench</h3>
      <a href="/activities/" class="ml-auto text-xs text-purple-400 hover:underline">Practice →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Save any word to your personal flash card deck. Review them with auto-play, filter by category, and test yourself under time pressure. Spaced repetition built into your Scrabble practice — the same technique language learners use to memorise thousands of words. Your WordBench grows with you, becoming your personal dictionary of mastered vocabulary.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tool: Word Quiz -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/10 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="text-lg">🧠</span>
      <h3 class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Word Quiz</h3>
      <a href="/activities/#quiz" class="ml-auto text-xs text-blue-400 hover:underline">Play →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Match words to their meanings under time pressure. Choose your difficulty, pick from your own WordBench categories, and watch your accuracy climb. Lex AI analyses your quiz history and coaches you on weak areas. This is active recall — the single most effective learning technique science has discovered.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tool: 60-Second -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="text-lg">⏱️</span>
      <h3 class="text-green-400 font-semibold">60-Second Word Finder</h3>
      <a href="/sixty-seconds/" class="ml-auto text-xs text-green-400 hover:underline">Play →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Seven random tiles. Sixty seconds. How many words can you find? This game trains the exact skill you need in live Scrabble: spotting valid words under time pressure. Your speed will triple within a week of daily practice. Personal bests tracked. Leaderboard for competitive spirits.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tool: Cows & Bulls -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-orange-500/30 bg-orange-950/10 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="text-lg">🐄</span>
      <h3 class="text-orange-400 font-semibold">Cows & Bulls</h3>
      <a href="/activities/#cab" class="ml-auto text-xs text-orange-400 hover:underline">Play →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Deduce a secret word through logical elimination — like Wordle meets Mastermind. Builds your letter-position awareness and vocabulary simultaneously. Choose 4-7 letter words, play with a timer, or use your own WordBench dictionary. Every round teaches you new words by forcing you to think through possibilities.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tool: Daily Challenges -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="text-lg">📅</span>
      <h3 class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">Daily Challenges</h3>
      <a href="/activities/" class="ml-auto text-xs text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Today's →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong>Word of the Day</strong> — learn one powerful word every day with meaning, etymology, and usage. <strong>Daily Rack</strong> — the same 7 tiles for everyone; find the highest-scoring word and compete globally. <strong>Daily Anagram</strong> — unscramble a word with Wordle-style colour feedback. Three daily habits that compound into massive vocabulary growth over months.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tool: Magic Squares -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/30 bg-indigo-950/10 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="text-lg">🪄</span>
      <h3 class="text-indigo-400 font-semibold">Magic Squares</h3>
      <a href="/magic-squares/" class="ml-auto text-xs text-indigo-400 hover:underline">Play →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">A number puzzle that exercises logical deduction and constraint satisfaction — the same mental muscles you use for Scrabble board positioning. Choose 4×4, 5×5, or 6×6 grids across multiple difficulty levels. Pure brain training in a different flavour.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tool: Lex AI Coach -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-950/20 to-blue-950/10 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <img src="/lex-avatar-32.png" alt="Lex" width="20" height="20" class="rounded-full" />
      <h3 class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">Lex — Your AI Scrabble Coach</h3>
      <a href="/chat/" class="ml-auto text-xs text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Chat →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Ask Lex anything about Scrabble strategy, word definitions, rack evaluation, or game tactics. Powered by AI with retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) — Lex searches our entire library of 1,000+ strategy articles and dictionary data to give you expert-level answers instantly. Lex also coaches you after quizzes and games, identifying patterns in your play and suggesting targeted improvements.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tool: Blog & Knowledge Base -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-600/30 bg-gray-800/20 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="text-lg">📖</span>
      <h3 class="text-gray-300 font-semibold">1,000+ Strategy Articles</h3>
      <a href="/blog/" class="ml-auto text-xs text-gray-400 hover:underline">Browse →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">From beginner guides to tournament-level tactics. Two-letter word lists, bingo stems, hook words, rack management, tile tracking, opening strategy, endgame technique — every aspect of Scrabble mastery covered in depth. All searchable, all free.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tool: World Rankings -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10 p-5 mb-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="text-lg">🌍</span>
      <h3 class="text-amber-400 font-semibold">World Scrabble Rankings</h3>
      <a href="/world-rankings/" class="ml-auto text-xs text-amber-400 hover:underline">View →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Follow the world's best players. Track rating changes, explore country statistics, discover player career timelines. Get inspired by the elite and understand what separates good from great.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- The Path -->
  <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Your Path to Mastery</h2>

  <div class="space-y-4 my-6">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
      <span class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-purple-300 font-bold">1</span>
      <div>
        <p class="text-purple-300 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Start with the Solver</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Enter your tiles every time you play. See what you missed. Notice the patterns. Your brain starts recognising common letter combinations automatically.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
      <span class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-purple-300 font-bold">2</span>
      <div>
        <p class="text-purple-300 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Build Your WordBench</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Save every word that surprises you. Build categorised dictionaries — two-letter words, Q-without-U words, bingo stems. Review them daily with flash cards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
      <span class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-purple-300 font-bold">3</span>
      <div>
        <p class="text-purple-300 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Practice Under Pressure</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Play the 60-Second game daily. Take quizzes from your WordBench. Solve the Daily Rack. Time pressure builds the speed you need in real games.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
      <span class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-purple-300 font-bold">4</span>
      <div>
        <p class="text-purple-300 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Learn Strategy</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Read our strategy guides. Understand rack management, tile tracking, board control, and endgame tactics. Ask Lex for personalised coaching on your weak areas.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
      <span class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-purple-300 font-bold">5</span>
      <div>
        <p class="text-purple-300 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Compete & Track Progress</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Climb the leaderboards. Earn stars and badges. Track your quiz accuracy over time. Watch your scores rise as vocabulary and speed improve together.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- For Everyone -->
  <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Something for Everyone</h2>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6">
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
      <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏠 Family Game Night</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Settle disputes instantly, learn new words together, and make every game more fun and educational for all ages.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/10">
      <p class="text-blue-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🧓 Keeping Your Mind Sharp</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Word games are one of the best exercises for cognitive health. A few minutes of daily practice strengthens memory, recall speed, and mental flexibility.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
      <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏆 Tournament Preparation</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Study word lists systematically, practice under time pressure, analyse your performance, and enter your first tournament with confidence.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
      <p class="text-purple-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">📖 Vocabulary Building</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Whether you're learning English or just love words, our tools make vocabulary acquisition effortless and enjoyable through daily exposure and active recall.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Closing statement -->
  <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-green-500/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-950/20 to-emerald-950/10 p-8 mt-10 text-center">
    <p class="text-lg text-white font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Every word you learn is a permanent upgrade to your game. Every day you practice makes the next game easier. <span class="text-green-400 font-semibold">Start today. Start free. Start now.</span>
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-500 text-white font-bold text-sm transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-green-900/30">🔍 Open the Word Solver →</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Back link -->
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to Home</a>
  </div>

</div>
</Layout>
